<p>[:en]</p>
<h1 id="about-game-name">About Game Name</h1>
<p>In this slot we head out to the American countryside. Amongst cow, pigs, sheep and chickens you’re forced to buckle down to avoid getting swept away by the raging tornados that plague this farm. The slot is fully packed with humor and Wilds which makes this a refreshing slot to play.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game features</h2>
<p>Tornado Farm Escape is played on the standard five reels, three row with 20 bet lines. The game is generous with the wilds, it also comes withw two nice special features where the focus is on the Wild symbols.</p>
<h3 id="wild">Wild</h3>
<p>The Wild symbols act as all symbols except the Hot and Cold symbols.</p>
<h3 id="tornado">Tornado</h3>
<p>This is the signature feature of this slot, when a Hot symbol appears on the first reel at the same time as a Cold comes up on the fifth the Tornado feature activates. This causes a tornado to appear that collects any occurrence of the symbol in the center of the board plus all wilds. After the tornado has collected all symbols it triggers a re-spin, this continues until the tornado is unable to find a target.</p>
<h3 id="storm">Storm</h3>
<p>This feature is randomly activated on a normal spin.<br>
The storm appears as a dark storm cloud moving randomly across the reels turning normal symbols into Wilds. Once the storm is done transforming symbols it leaves the screen leaving behind the Wilds it created and quite possibly a big win.</p>
<h2 id="game-details">Game details</h2>
